org.anchoranalysis.math.arithmetic

Class RunningSumMap<T>

  • Object
    • RunningSumMap<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - unique identifier.

    public class RunningSumMap<T>
extends Object
    A map of unique identifiers to RunningSum instances.

    The map is initially empty, and when an unrecognised identifier is passed to the get(T) function, then it is added to the map.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
